-You had the experiences before.

01:14:10.710 --> 01:14:12.708
Not this one.

01:14:13.017 --> 01:14:15.616
My life has always been so
contolled.

01:14:17.224 --> 01:14:19.523
-And it will be again.
-Sure, of course.

01:14:20.532 --> 01:14:23.430
